name: Transcicada
desc: If this card is Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 “Husk Token” (EARTH/Insect/Level 3/0 ATK/0 DEF). As long as the token Special Summoned by this effect remains in a Monster Zone, you cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck, except Insect monsters. You can only use this effect of "Transcicada" once per turn.
